852
01:21:44,800 --> 01:21:46,200
But...

853
01:21:47,000 --> 01:21:48,800
...what about us?

854
01:21:49,600 --> 01:21:51,200
What about us?

855
01:21:53,800 --> 01:21:56,200
You think that...

856
01:21:56,400 --> 01:21:58,800
...maybe we can...

857
01:21:59,000 --> 01:22:02,000
