how you feel about me.

859
01:22:09,200 --> 01:22:12,200
-Yes, you do.
-No, I don't.

860
01:22:13,800 --> 01:22:15,400
Yes, you do.

861
01:22:15,600 --> 01:22:17,200
You're gonna go off to vet school...

862
01:22:17,400 --> 01:22:20,600
...find some vet and do
some animal experiments.

863
01:22:21,000 --> 01:22:23,600
Dissect animals and....

