879
01:25:11,600 --> 01:25:14,800
I'm not gonna lie to you,
this is a big night.

880
01:25:15,800 --> 01:25:18,000
But all those people out there...

881
01:25:18,200 --> 01:25:21,400
...they're your friends, they're your
