939
01:30:20,200 --> 01:30:23,200
Now you get up there
and you be fantastic for you.

940
01:30:24,200 --> 01:30:25,800
-Right, for yourself.
-For yourself.

941
01:30:27,000 --> 01:30:29,800
And now let's give it up
for El Gran Colectivo!

942
01:30:30,200 --> 01:30:32,200
-Yeah. Screw him.
-Yeah!

943
01:30:34,000 --> 01:30:35,600
